The '''Flip of the Credit''' was a [[Casino/Legends|casino]] owned by the [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] [[Avaro Sookcool]]. It was located in [[Equator City/Legends|Equator City]] on [[Rodia/Legends|the Rodian homeworld]] and served as a front for money laundering conducted by [[Black Sun/Legends|Black Sun]]. [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] met with Avaro here in order to solicit the criminal syndicate's aid in finding and rescuing the captured [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]]. Her opinion of it was that it was a "ninth-rate, [[Insect/Legends|bug]]-chewed casino."

